.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH diagnose 1  "diagnose "
.SH NAME
diagnose \- Pre\-automation challenge scan (iframes, overlays, media gates, frameworks, patterns)
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdiagnose\fR [\fB\-\-current\fR] [\fB\-\-wait\-until\fR] [\fB\-\-timeout\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fIURL\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Scan a page for automation challenges — iframes, overlay blockers, shadow DOM, canvas/WebGL rendering, media playback gates, and framework\-specific interaction quirks — plus named\-pattern matches (e.g., Storyline acc\-blocker, SCORM player, React portal) with actionable agentchrome command suggestions. Accepts a URL to navigate\-then\-analyze, or `\-\-current` to analyze the already\-loaded page in place.
.PP
OUTPUT SCHEMA (JSON on stdout):
{
"url": string,
"scope": "diagnosed" | "current",
"challenges": [{category, severity, summary, details, suggestion?}],
"patterns":   [{name, matched, confidence, evidence, suggestion}],
"summary":    {challengeCount, patternMatchCount, hasHighSeverity, straightforward}
}
.PP
EXIT CODES: 0 success; 1 general/arg errors; 2 connection; 3 target; 4 timeout; 5 protocol.
.PP
Note: <url> and \-\-current are mutually exclusive. Exactly one must be provided.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-current\fR
Diagnose the already\-loaded page in the active tab without navigating (mutually exclusive with <url>)
.TP
\fB\-\-wait\-until\fR \fI<WAIT_UNTIL>\fR [default: load]
Wait strategy after navigation (URL mode only; ignored with \-\-current)
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
load: Wait for the load event
.IP \(bu 2
domcontentloaded: Wait for DOMContentLoaded event
.IP \(bu 2
networkidle: Wait until network is idle (no requests for 500ms)
.IP \(bu 2
none: Return immediately after initiating navigation
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-timeout\fR \fI<TIMEOUT>\fR
Navigation timeout in milliseconds (URL mode only; ignored with \-\-current)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
.TP
[\fIURL\fR]
URL to navigate to and diagnose (mutually exclusive with \-\-current)
.SH EXTRA
EXAMPLES:
  # Navigate to a URL and diagnose it for automation challenges
  agentchrome diagnose https://example.com/course

  # Diagnose the already\-loaded page in the active tab (no navigation)
  agentchrome diagnose \-\-current

  # Extract strategy suggestions using jq
  agentchrome diagnose \-\-current | jq \-r \*(Aq.patterns[].suggestion\*(Aq

  # Diagnose with network\-idle wait strategy
  agentchrome diagnose https://app.example.com \-\-wait\-until networkidle
.SH CAPABILITIES
.PP
Pre-automation challenge scan (iframes, overlays, media gates, frameworks, patterns)
.TP
.B diagnose <URL>
Pre-automation challenge scan (iframes, overlays, media gates, frameworks, patterns)
.TP
.B url
URL to navigate to and diagnose (mutually exclusive with --current)
.TP
.B --current
Diagnose the already-loaded page in the active tab without navigating (mutually exclusive with <url>)
.TP
.B --wait-until
Wait strategy after navigation (URL mode only; ignored with --current)
.TP
.B --timeout
Navigation timeout in milliseconds (URL mode only; ignored with --current)
.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
Examples:
.TP
.B \`agentchrome diagnose https://example.com/course\`
Navigate to a URL and diagnose it for automation challenges
.TP
.B \`agentchrome diagnose --current\`
Diagnose the already-loaded page without navigating
.TP
.B \`agentchrome diagnose --current | jq -r '.patterns[].suggestion'\`
Extract all pattern strategy suggestions via jq
.TP
.B \`agentchrome diagnose https://app.example.com --wait-until networkidle\`
Diagnose after waiting for network idle (for SPAs)
.TP
.B \`agentchrome diagnose --current | jq '.summary'\`
Check if the page is straightforward to automate
